{"title_page": "Ahmed Ghaleb Kadhim", "text_new": "{{Infobox person\n| name        = Ahmed Ghaleb Kadhim\n| image       = Ahmed Ghaleb Kadhim.jpg\n| caption     = Kadhim in 2019\n| birth_date  = {{birth-date and age|6 December 1989}}\n| birth_place = [[Baghdad, Iraq]]\n| occupation  = Civil activist, activist against electronic blackmail, journalist\n}}\nAhmed Ghaleb Kadhim (arabic \u0627\u062d\u0645\u062f \u063a\u0627\u0644\u0628 \u0643\u0627\u0638\u0645), born in Iraq 6 December 1989, is known as the Best Arab activist against electronic blackmail.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bUGRNSoKSyo&feature=youtu.be|title=Ahmed Ghaleb|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7nnn_m1y_Iw&feature=youtu.be|title=Electronic Blackmail|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C52zUCS6X9s&feature=youtu.be|title=The unfair Network|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> He was part of the peaceful demonistration that started the 1st of October 2019 against the Iraqi government. He was kidnapped by unknown people because of his active role in the demonstration. <ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.menarights.org/en/caseprofile/peaceful-protestor-and-activist-ahmed-al-zubaidi-disappeared-abduction-december-26-2019|title=Peaceful protestor and activist Ahmed Al Zubaidi disappeared since abduction on December 26, 2019 {{!}} MENA Rights Group|website=www.menarights.org|language=en|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elbyan.com/%d8%a3%d8%ae%d8%aa%d8%b7%d8%a7%d9%81-%d8%a7%d8%ad%d9%85%d8%af-%d8%a7%d9%84%d8%ba%d8%a7%d9%84%d8%a8-%d8%a7%d9%81%d8%b6%d9%84-%d9%85%d8%ad%d8%a7%d8%b1%d8%a8-%d8%b9%d8%b1%d8%a8%d9%89-%d9%84%d9%84%d8%a7/|title=\u0623\u062e\u062a\u0637\u0627\u0641 \u0627\u062d\u0645\u062f \u0627\u0644\u063a\u0627\u0644\u0628 \u0627\u0641\u0636\u0644 \u0645\u062d\u0627\u0631\u0628 \u0639\u0631\u0628\u0649 \u0644\u0644\u0627\u0628\u062a\u0632\u0627\u0632 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0644\u0643\u062a\u0631\u0648\u0646\u0649|date=2019-12-28|website=\u062c\u0631\u064a\u062f\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0627\u0646|language=en|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref> \n\n== Ahmed's life ==\nAhmed was born in [[Baghdad]] 1989 in a small family. \n\nThe Arab Women Media Network, whose membership includes 18 Arab countries, chose Iraqi journalist Ahmed Ghaleb Kazem Known as \"Ahmed Al-Ghaleb\" the best fighter for e-blackmail in the Arab world. Ahmed Ghaleb is the best fighter for electronic blackmail due to his successes in this regard, especially that the Arab media and the international benefit from his experiences in its television programs as he is a professional information security researcher despite his young age.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elbyan.com/%d8%b4%d8%a8%d9%83%d8%a9-%d8%a7%d8%b9%d9%84%d8%a7%d9%85-%d8%a7%d9%84%d9%85%d8%b1%d8%a3%d8%a9-%d8%a7%d9%84%d8%b9%d8%b1%d8%a8%d9%8a%d8%a9-%d8%aa%d8%ae%d8%aa%d8%a7%d8%b1-%d8%a7%d9%84%d8%b5%d8%ad%d9%81/|title=\u0634\u0628\u0643\u0629 \u0627\u0639\u0644\u0627\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0631\u0623\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0631\u0628\u064a\u0629 \u062a\u062e\u062a\u0627\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u062d\u0641\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0631\u0627\u0642\u0649 \u0627\u062d\u0645\u062f \u063a\u0627\u0644\u0628 \u0627\u0641\u0636\u0644 \u0645\u062d\u0627\u0631\u0628 \u0639\u0631\u0628\u0649 \u0644\u0644\u0627\u0628\u062a\u0632\u0627\u0632 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0644\u0643\u062a\u0631\u0648\u0646\u0649|date=2019-12-25|website=\u062c\u0631\u064a\u062f\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u064a\u0627\u0646|language=en|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref> He was rewarded the best Activist against electronic blackmail in December 2019.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://aldaae.com/%d8%a7%d9%84%d8%b5%d8%ad%d9%81%d9%8a-%d8%a7%d9%84%d8%b9%d8%b1%d8%a7%d9%82%d9%8a-%d8%a7%d8%ad%d9%85%d8%af-%d8%ba%d8%a7%d9%84%d8%a8-%d8%a7%d9%81%d8%b6%d9%84-%d9%85%d8%ad%d8%a7%d8%b1%d8%a8-%d8%b9%d8%b1/|title=\u0627\u0644\u0635\u062d\u0641\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0631\u0627\u0642\u064a \u0627\u062d\u0645\u062f \u063a\u0627\u0644\u0628 \u0627\u0641\u0636\u0644 \u0645\u062d\u0627\u0631\u0628 \u0639\u0631\u0628\u0649 \u0644\u0644\u0627\u0628\u062a\u0632\u0627\u0632 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0644\u0643\u062a\u0631\u0648\u0646\u0649|website=\u0627\u0644\u062f\u0627\u0639\u064a \u0646\u064a\u0648\u0632|language=ar|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.elaosboa.news/22618|title=\u0625\u0639\u0644\u0627\u0645 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u0631\u0623\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0631\u0628\u064a\u0629 \u062a\u062e\u062a\u0627\u0631 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u062d\u0641\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0631\u0627\u0642\u0649 \u0623\u062d\u0645\u062f \u063a\u0627\u0644\u0628 \u0623\u0641\u0636\u0644 \u0645\u062d\u0627\u0631\u0628 \u0639\u0631\u0628\u0649 \u0644\u0644\u0627\u0628\u062a\u0632\u0627\u0632 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0644\u0643\u062a\u0631\u0648\u0646\u0649|website=\u0628\u0648\u0627\u0628\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0633\u0628\u0648\u0639|language=ar|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref>\n\nDue to his participation in the demonistration against the Iraqi government, Ahmed was kidnapped in Baghdad in 26th of December 2019 by unknown group.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sadaelomma.com/\u063a\u0636\u0628-\u0641\u0649-\u0627\u0644\u0639\u0631\u0627\u0642-\u0644\u0627\u062e\u062a\u0637\u0627\u0641-\u0627\u062d\u0645\u062f-\u0627\u0644\u063a\u0627\u0644\u0628-\u0627\u0641\u0636\u0644/|title=\u063a\u0636\u0628 \u0641\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0631\u0627\u0642 \u0644\u0627\u062e\u062a\u0637\u0627\u0641 \u0627\u062d\u0645\u062f \u0627\u0644\u063a\u0627\u0644\u0628 \u0627\u0641\u0636\u0644 \u0645\u062d\u0627\u0631\u0628 \u0639\u0631\u0628\u0649 \u0644\u0644\u0627\u0628\u062a\u0632\u0627\u0632 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u0644\u0643\u062a\u0631\u0648\u0646\u0649|date=2019-12-28|website=\u0635\u062f\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u0645\u0629|language=ar|access-date=2020-04-03}}</ref>\n\nOn December 26, 2019, Ahmed was on his way home when he was suddenly kidnapped by a group of armed men wearing civilian clothes and forced into the trunk of a black SUV vehicle. His kidnapping was filmed by a camera installed in the neighbourhood where he normally resides. <ref name=\":0\" />\n\nIn March 2020 he was released with no major injury.\n\n== References ==\n<!-- Inline citations added to your article will automatically display here. See en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WP:REFB for instructions on how to add citations. -->\n{{reflist}}\n\n\n{{Iraq-bio-stub}}\n[[Category:1989 births]]\n[[Category:Iraqi journalists]]\n[[Category:Iraqi activists]]\n[[Category:People from Baghdad]]\n[[Category:Iraqi bloggers]]\n[[Category:Electronic Blackmail]]\n[[Category:Kidnapping]]\n[[Category:Iraqi protest]]\n[[Category:Ahmed Ghaleb]]\n", "text_old": "Ahmed Ghaleb Kadhim (arabic \u0627\u062d\u0645\u062f \u063a\u0627\u0644\u0628 \u0643\u0627\u0638\u0645) , born in Iraq the 6th of December 1989, is known as the Best Arab activist against electronic blackmail.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bUGRNSoKSyo&feature=youtu.be|title=Ahmed Ghaleb|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7nnn_m1y_Iw&feature=youtu.be|title=Electronic Blackmail|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C52zUCS6X9s&feature=youtu.be|title=The unfair Network|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> He was part of the peaceful demonistration that started the 1st of October 2019 against the Iraqi government. He was kidnapped by unknown people because of his active role in the demonstration. <ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.menarights.org/en