ani]]</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flagcountry|MEX}}\n| [[Senate of the Republic (Mexico)|Senate of the Republic]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|0|128|hex=red}}\n| [[Chamber of Deputies (Mexico)|Chamber of Deputies]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|3|500|hex=red}}\n| \n|-\n| {{flagcountry|MAR}}\n|[[House of Councillors (Morocco)|House of Councillors]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|0|120|hex=red}}\n|[[House of Representatives (Morocco)|House of Representatives]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|1|395|hex=red}}<ref>[[Abdelkader Aamara]], MP for [[Sal\u00e9]]</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flagcountry|MON}}\n|Align=center|\n|[[National Council (Monaco)|National Council]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|0|24|hex=red}}\n|\n|-\n|{{flagcountry|Nigeria}}\n|[[Senate of Nigeria|Senate]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|0|109|hex=red}}\n|[[House of Representatives (Nigeria)|House of Representatives]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|0|360|hex=red}}\n|\n|-\n| {{flagcountry|NOR}}\n|Align=center|\n|[[Storting]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|0|169|hex=red}}\n|\n|-\n| {{flagcountry|PHI}}\n|[[Senate of the Philippines|Senate]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|3|24|hex=red}}<ref>[[Juan Miguel Zubiri]]<br>[[Koko Pimentel]]<br>[[Sonny Angara]]</ref>\n|[[House of Representatives of the Philippines|House of Representatives]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|1|303|hex=red}}<ref>Henry Villarica</ref>\n|\n|-\n|{{flagcountry|Poland}}\n|[[Senate of Poland|Senate]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|0|100|hex=red}}\n|[[Sejm]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|0|460|hex=red}}\n|\n|-\n|{{flagcountry|ESP}}\n|\n|[[Congress of Deputies]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|5|350|hex=red}}<ref>[[Javier Ortega Smith]]<br>[[Santiago Abascal]]<br>Macarena Olona<br>Beatriz Jim\u00e9nez</ref>\n|[[Parliament of Navarre]] {{Composition bar compact|1|50|hex=red}}\n|-\n|{{flagcountry|South Africa}}\n|[[National Council of Provinces]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|0|90|hex=red}}\n|[[National Assembly of South Africa|National Assembly]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|1|400|hex=red}}