ara]], District 17</ref><br>[[New Jersey General Assembly]] {{Composition bar compact|1|80|hex=red}}<ref>[[Clinton Calabrese]], District 36</ref><br>[[Oklahoma Senate|Oklahoma State Senate]] {{Composition bar compact|1|48|hex=red}}<ref>Paul Rosino, District 45</ref><br>[[Oklahoma House of Representatives]] {{Composition bar compact|1|101|hex=red}}<ref>Jason Lowe, District 97</ref><br>[[Missouri House of Representatives]] {{Composition bar compact|1|163|hex=red}}<ref>[[Joe Runions]], District 37</ref><br>[[Michigan House of Representatives]] {{Composition bar compact|1|110|hex=red}}<ref>Tyrone Carter, District 6</ref><br>{{Composition bar compact|1|110|hex=black}}<ref>[[Isaac Robinson (politician)|Isaac Robinson]], District 4</ref><br>[[South Dakota House of Representatives]] {{Composition bar compact|1|70|hex=black}}<ref>[[Bob Glanzer]], District 22</ref><br>[[Massachusetts House of Representatives]]  {{Composition bar compact|1|160|hex=red}}<ref>Michael Day, District 31</ref>\n|-\n|{{flagcountry|UK}}\n|[[House of Lords]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|0|789|hex=red}}\n|[[House of Commons of the United Kingdom|House of Commons]]<br>{{Composition bar compact|6|635|hex=red}}<ref>[[Nadine Dorries]], [[Member of Parliament (United Kingdom)|MP]] for [[Mid Bedfordshire (UK Parliament constituency)|Mid Bedfordshire]]<br />[[Kate Osborne]], [[Member of Parliament (United Kingdom)|MP]] for [[Jarrow (UK Parliament constituency)|Jarrow]]<br />[[Lloyd Russell-Moyle]], [[Member of Parliament (United Kingdom)|MP]] for [[Brighton Kemptown (UK Parliament constituency)|Brighton Kemptown]], <br />[[Boris Johnson]], [[Member of Parliament (United Kingdom)|MP]] for [[Uxbridge and South Ruislip (UK Parliament constituency)|Uxbridge and South Ruislip]]<br />[[Matt Hancock]], [[Member of Parliament (United Kingdom)|MP]] for [[West Suffolk (UK Parliament constituency)|West Suffolk]]<br>[[Alister Jack]], [[Member of Parliament (United Kingdom)|MP]] for [[Dumfries and Galloway (UK Parliament c