t]].\n*Air Marshal [[Anthony Bagnall|Anthony John Crowther Bagnall]], {{post-nominals|country=GBR|CB|OBE}}, [[Royal Air Force]].\n\n:;Civil Division\n*[[Richard Mottram|Richard Clive Mottram]], Permanent Secretary, [[Ministry of Defence (United Kingdom)|Ministry of Defence]].\n*[[Hayden Phillips|Gerald Hayden Phillips]], {{post-nominals|country=GBR|CB}}, Permanent Secretary, [[Department for Culture, Media and Sport]].\n\n====Companions (CB)====\n:;Military Division\n*Vice Admiral Michael Peter Gretton.\n*Rear Admiral David John Wood.\n*Major General [[Jonathan Hall (British Army officer)|Jonathan Michael Francis Cooper Hall]], {{post-nominals|country=GBR|OBE}}, (480320), late The [[Royal Scots Dragoon Guards]].\n*Major General William John Pherrick Robins, {{post-nominals|country=GBR|OBE}}, (469087), late [[Royal Corps of Signals]].\n*Major General [[Charles Vyvyan|Charles Gerard Courtenay Vyvyan]], {{post-nominals|country=GBR|CBE}}, (484776), late The [[Royal Green Jackets]].\n*Air Vice-Marshal David Anthony Hurrell, {{post-nominals|country=GBR|AFC}}, [[Royal Air Force]].\n*Air Vice-Marshal [[Peter Millar (RAF officer)|Peter Millar]], Royal Air Force.\n\n:;Civil Division\n*Geoffrey Hubert Bush, Director General, Resources and Planning, Her Majesty's [[Board of Inland Revenue]].\n*Richard John Derek Garden, Head, Food Safety and Environment Directorate, [[Ministry of Agriculture, Fisheries and Food]].\n*Romola Carol Andrea Christopherson, Director of Press and Publicity, [[Department of Health and Social Care|Department of Health]].\n*David Lovell Foot, Forestry Commissioner, [[Forestry Commission]].\n*Brian Michael Fox, Director, Senior Civil Service Group, [[Cabinet Office]] (Office of Public Service).\n*James Hamill, Head, Home Department, [[Scottish Office]].\n*Julian David Hansen, lately Band 7, Ministry of Defence.\n*Samuel Alexander Harbison, HM Chief Inspector of Nuclear Installations and Director of Nuclear Safety, [[Health and Safety Executive]].\n*John C